<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Vérification du code - Coursia Admin</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --coursia-orange: #F97316;
            --coursia-orange-hover: #EA580C;
            --coursia-dark: #020617;
            --coursia-gray: #E5E7EB;
        }
        * { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
        body {
            background: #F5F5F5;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .login-container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.15), 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1), 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            width: 75%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            height: 75vh;
            min-height: 500px;
        }
        .login-illustration {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--coursia-orange) 0%, #FB923C 100%);
            flex: 0 0 50%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 40px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .login-illustration::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%; left: -50%;
            width: 200%; height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
        }
        .illustration-content { position: relative; z-index: 1; text-align: center; color: white; }
        .illustration-icon { font-size: 100px; margin-bottom: 25px; opacity: 0.9; }
        .illustration-title { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .illustration-text { font-size: 15px; opacity: 0.9; max-width: 280px; line-height: 1.6; }
        .login-form-section {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 50px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            background: #FAFBFC;
        }
        .brand-logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        .brand-logo i { font-size: 28px; color: var(--coursia-orange); }
        .brand-logo span { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--coursia-dark); }
        .login-title { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--coursia-dark); margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .login-subtitle { color: #6B7280; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 35px; }
        .form-label { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: #6B7280; margin-bottom: 6px; }
        .form-control {
            border: none;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--coursia-gray);
            border-radius: 0;
            padding: 12px 0;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: border-color 0.3s;
            background: transparent;
        }
        .form-control:focus { box-shadow: none; border-color: var(--coursia-orange); background: transparent; }
        .form-control::placeholder { color: #9CA3AF; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; font-weight: 400; }
        .btn-coursia {
            background: var(--coursia-orange);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            padding: 14px 35px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: white;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .btn-coursia:hover { background: var(--coursia-orange-hover); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(249,115,22,0.3); }
        .btn-coursia i { margin-left: 8px; }
        .alert { border-radius: 12px; border: none; font-size: 14px; }
        .alert-danger { background: #FEE2E2; color: #991B1B; }
        .no-account { text-align: center; margin-top: 25px; color: #6B7280; font-size: 14px; }
        .no-account a { color: var(--coursia-orange); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--coursia-orange); padding-bottom: 2px; transition: all 0.3s; }
        .no-account a:hover { color: var(--coursia-orange-hover); border-bottom-color: var(--coursia-orange-hover); }
        .steps { display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .step { flex: 1; height: 4px; border-radius: 2px; background: var(--coursia-gray); }
        .step.active { background: var(--coursia-orange); }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .login-container { width: 95%; height: auto; min-height: auto; }
            .login-illustration { display: none; }
            .login-form-section { padding: 40px 30px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="login-container">
        <div class="login-illustration">
            <div class="illustration-content">
                <div class="illustration-icon"><i class="bi bi-phone"></i></div>
                <h2 class="illustration-title">Code SMS envoyé</h2>
                <p class="illustration-text">Vérifiez vos SMS et saisissez le code à 6 chiffres reçu. Il est valable 1 heure.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="login-form-section">
            <div class="brand-logo">
                <i class="bi bi-box-seam"></i>
                <span>Coursia</span>
            </div>

            <div class="steps">
                <div class="step active"></div>
                <div class="step active"></div>
                <div class="step"></div>
            </div>

            <h1 class="login-title">Vérification du code</h1>
            <p class="login-subtitle">Saisissez le code à 6 chiffres reçu par SMS.</p>

            {% if error %}
                <div class="alert alert-danger mb-4">
                    <i class="bi bi-exclamation-circle me-2"></i>{{ error }}
                </div>
            {% endif %}

            <form method="POST" action="{{ path('admin_reset_verify') }}">
                <div class="mb-4">
                    <label class="form-label">CODE DE VÉRIFICATION</label>
                    <input type="text" name="code" class="form-control" placeholder="000000"
                           maxlength="6" pattern="[0-9]{6}" inputmode="numeric"
                           autocomplete="one-time-code" required autofocus>
                </div>

                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-coursia mt-3">
                    Vérifier le code <i class="bi bi-check-lg"></i>
                </button>

                <p class="no-account">
                    <a href="{{ path('admin_forgot_password') }}"><i class="bi bi-arrow-left me-1"></i>Renvoyer un code</a>
                </p>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
